From dream to reality.
 
@rebeccalongendyke wears COCO CRUSH and COLLECTION N°5 earrings, a necklace and rings in BEIGE GOLD set with diamonds, as well as the PREMIÈRE GALON watch in 18K yellow gold.
 
@mona_tougaard wears earrings, a necklace, a bracelet and a ring from the CAMÉLIA collection in yellow gold set with diamonds, as well as the PREMIÈRE ÉDITION ORIGINALE watch in 0.1-micron yellow gold-plated steel.
 
For the holidays, CHANEL makes the most precious dreams come true.
 
